c: 66
v: 11
t: "And Allah has set forth an example for those who believe, the wife of Fir'aun (Pharaoh), when she said: \"My Lord! Build for me a home with You in Paradise, and save me from Fir'aun (Pharaoh) and his work, and save me from the people who are Zalimun (polytheists, wrong-doers and disbelievers in Allah)"